619
00:30:06,445 --> 00:30:08,581
- The price can't reflect on a gown

620
00:30:08,581 --> 00:30:10,748
that's a timeless classic.

621
00:30:11,986 --> 00:30:14,794
- Yeah, a '57 roadster
is a timeless classic

622
00:30:14,794 --> 00:30:17,487
