00:32:55,577 --> 00:32:56,410
Oh God.

668
00:33:01,188 --> 00:33:04,188
(crickets chirping)

669
00:33:27,174 --> 00:33:29,841
(Mary laughing)

670
00:33:30,859 --> 00:33:31,692
- Busted.

