00:33:36,731 --> 00:33:39,318
Look, I didn't get home in
time to stoke the stove,

674
00:33:39,318 --> 00:33:40,818
so I, I got stuck.

675
00:33:45,406 --> 00:33:47,989
(gentle music)

676
00:34:09,720 --> 00:34:10,887
- I better go.

677
00:34:15,666 --> 00:34:18,833
(Ken blows raspberry)

