00:38:42,850 --> 00:38:44,900
- Yes, yes it was.
- For an old guy.

765
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:47,558
- What!
- Yeah (laughs).

766
00:38:47,558 --> 00:38:49,092
- For an old guy?
- For an old guy.

767
00:38:49,092 --> 00:38:51,072
- [John] Listen, man,
I went three for three.

768
00:38:51,072 --> 00:38:52,299
You know that that means, three for three,

