786
00:39:26,857 --> 00:39:28,680
You couldn't take care of your own kids.

787
00:39:28,680 --> 00:39:30,519
- Thanks, I'll take over.

788
00:39:30,519 --> 00:39:32,936
- Everything's under control.

789
00:39:34,396 --> 00:39:36,784
